;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/iOgz6euzBNqhvJyhCgG5bQrCQzs=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873 /cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73604681/247263_iphone_16_pro_AKrales_0324.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;If3mFS ”多年来，我们一直在 &lt;em>;The Verg&lt;/em>;e 追踪摄影的缓慢重新定义 - 我很确定我们已经开始了“什么是照片”的争论，因为它与智能手机摄影有关&lt;em>;The Vergecast&lt;/em>; 2018 年的某个时间，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/11/1/20942673/google-instagram-vergecast-robby-stein-isaac- reynolds&quot;>;2019 年该主题的现场表演&lt;/a>;。但今年情况开始快速变化，越来越多的公司推出人工智能工具，完全重新定义了摄影过程每一步图像的制作方式，来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 7/26/24206969/google-pixel-9-add-me-group-photos-leak&quot;>;构图&lt;/a>;到 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/3/13/ 23637401/samsung-fake-moon-photos-ai-galaxy-s21-s23-ultra&quot;>;捕获&lt;/a>;到 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/21/24224084/ google-pixel-9-reimagine-ai-photos&quot;>;编辑&lt;/a>;。我们已经写过&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24199005/samsung-galaxy-ai-z-fold-6-sketch-to-image&quot;>;其中一些工具&lt;/a>;以及它们的功能，我们发布了一些文章来解释这些工具的广泛可用性如何产生影响&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24242800/ai-image-editing -photoshop-misinformation-deepfakes-elon-musk-grok-decoder-interview&quot;>;有意义的不同&lt;/a>; — &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/22/24225972/ai- photo-era-what-is-reality-google-pixel-9&quot;>;比&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/26/24228808/ai 更危险&lt;/a>; -image-editing-photoshop-comparison-argument&quot;>;Photoshop 之类的工具&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;19dKN8&quot;>;但碰巧的是，高管们...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/23/24252231/lets-compare-apple-google-and-samsungs-definitions-of-a-photo&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/23/24252231/lets-compare-apple-google-and-samsungs-definitions-of-a-photo" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.t